ZH: 在病后，医生建议多喝泔水来调养身体。
EN: After an illness, doctors recommend drinking congee to nourish the body.

ZH: 泔水可以作为早餐、午餐或晚餐的选择。
EN: Congee can be a choice for breakfast, lunch, or dinner.

ZH: 我喜欢用豆浆代替水煮泔水。
EN: I like to use soy milk instead of water to cook congee.
